# Build context for `gcloud builds submit` (serving container).
#
# gcloud uses .gitignore when no .gcloudignore exists — and .gitignore excludes
# model.rds, which the serving Dockerfile needs (COPY model.rds). This file
# overrides that: keep model.rds in the build context while still excluding the
# things the build does not need.

.venv/
__pycache__/
*.ipynb
*.ipynb_checkpoints/
readme.md
uv.lock
pyproject.toml
*.yaml
